sources.description:
A cop is consumed with the desire to get revenge on the crook who shot & killed his wife during a robbery. The crook in question is Marseilles who is trying to assemble funds for his own retirement.

Original title: Squadra volante (1974)
Director: Stelvio Massi
Writers: Dardano Sacchetti, Gianfranco Barberi, Adriano Bolzoni
Stars: Tomas Milian, Gastone Moschin, Ray Lovelock
Genres: Action, Crime, Thriller
